commit.message: Add support to send C coverage. Don't cache. Move hex plugin to Action
Use COVERALLS environment variable to avoid on_load
Switch from Travis to Github Actions
Add Github Action to release in hex.pm when tagging

Instruct Dialyzer to discard some warnings

This module uses p1_options to change code of ets_cache_options
at run time, and thus Dialyzer raises some false alarms
Fix a pair of type specifications detected by Dialyzer

Add ability to specify custom timeout in lookup callbacks

This only works when cache life time is not set to infinity,
with infinity we never clean cache so this option is not respected.

Merge pull request #22 from santosh653/master
